# Impact

Reverse-dependency analysis. Use before changing a file or package
to see what else depends on it.

1. Ask the user for the file path or import path.
2. Run `gofasta impact <target> --json`.
3. Report `direct_importers`, `transitive_importers`, and
   `impacted_files`.
4. Use the impacted-file count to decide test scope; use the
   importer list to decide review scope.
